15 15 moveto (inside) show
gsave
  5 5 translate
  45 rotate
  0 0 10 10 box stroke
  20 20 moveto (inside) show
grestore
60 30 translate
scale-factor scale-factor scale
1 setlinewidth 1 setlinecap
/crosses 8 def
